reviewText: Was good to see Milton Berle. A good clean comedy act, with plenty of variety.

This is the first program of the seventh year and is sponsored by Buick.  Although it is a sometimes amusing comedy between Berle and Andy Rooney it is not a good example of what the Berle show was all about.  No Texaco men,  no wild entry, no variety of acts.  This is not an example of Berle at his  zany best.
